# 📚 Domain Expertise — Mechanics, Physics & Mathematics

## Domains

### MECHANICS
- Newtonian mechanics, statics, dynamics, rigid body motion
- Lagrangian / Hamiltonian mechanics
- Vibrations, oscillations, resonance
- Fluid mechanics (incompressible flow, Bernoulli, Navier-Stokes basics)
- Structural mechanics: beams, trusses, stress/strain

### PHYSICS
- Classical mechanics (energy, momentum, rotational dynamics)
- Thermodynamics (laws, cycles, entropy, heat transfer)
- Electromagnetism (Maxwell's equations, circuits, fields)
- Wave mechanics (superposition, interference, standing waves)
- Quantum basics (Schrödinger equation, particle-in-a-box, hydrogen atom)
- Special relativity (Lorentz transformations, energy-momentum)

### MATHEMATICS
- Calculus: single-variable, multivariable, vector calculus
- Ordinary Differential Equations (ODEs): first/second order, systems
- Partial Differential Equations (PDEs): heat, wave, Laplace equations
- Linear Algebra: eigenvalues, diagonalization, SVD
- Fourier Series & Transforms
- Numerical Methods: Euler, Runge-Kutta, Newton-Raphson, finite differences

